author: Mat-Su Borough (info@www.akbizmag.com)
title: Glenn Highway offramp Palmer closed
text:
Glenn Highway offramp Palmer closed Starting October 3, 8 a.m. Mat-Su Borough October 2, 2015 
Glenn/Parks Highway Interchange northbound off-ramp closure 
(10/1/15)â€”A remediation contractor, working with the Alaska Department of Environmental Conservation, will close the northbound off-ramp (Milepost 35, Palmer/Wasilla Interchange) starting at 8 a.m. Saturday, Oct. 3. Work will include removing contaminated soils from the Sept. 4 fuel spill and fire, and restoring the roadway to its original condition. 
Crews will work as quickly as possible, and anticipate reopening the ramp early next week. Please use the Old Glenn Highway and Trunk Road as detours.
